 "Personal Write 4.1 - C. Selection of Printer Drivers"


C.         Selection of Printer Drivers


   The CBM_MPS1000, EpsonQ, EpsonX[CBM_MPS-1250], EpsonXOld, HP_LaserJet
and Nec_Pinwriter printer drivers are already contained in the "printers"
directory (in "devs") of the Personal Write program disk. Other drivers
can be copied from the Commodore Extras disk. The Commodore
"InstallPrinter" utility can be used to do so. The EpsonQ driver is
selected as the default driver. Other drivers can be selected with the
Amiga Preferences. Section 4.4 has more on this subject. The Cloanto
PostScript driver works in combination with any Amiga printer driver.

